01:22:44.599 --> 01:22:49.520
We'll split it together,
you and me, fifty-fifty.

01:22:51.231 --> 01:22:53.399
But I bet you didn't say you'd split on him.

01:22:53.650 --> 01:22:56.861
- It wasn't like that.
- Don't lie to me. Don't treat me like that.

01:22:57.111 --> 01:23:00.698
I bought it.

01:23:01.115 --> 01:23:03.660
What?

01:23:03.910 --> 01:23:06.829
I bought the tickets.
For her and for me. It was my idea.

01:23:07.080 --> 01:23:09.415
Your idea. I see.

01:23:09.666 --> 01:23:11.501
Well, that fits.

01:23:11.751 --> 01:23:16.464
I mean, you and him fit together.
I should have seen that a long time ago.

01:23:16.714 --> 01:23:19.801
- Alex, stop him!
- No, let him go. Let him have it all.

01:23:20.051 --> 01:23:24.055
Juliet, let him go.

01:23:25.890 --> 01:23:29.477
I'm leaving.

01:23:35.650 --> 01:23:42.156
You shouldn't have hit her! Do what
you like, but you shouldn't have hit her!

01:23:57.463 --> 01:24:00.675
