01:24:00.925 --> 01:24:02.218
You want it?

01:24:02.468 --> 01:24:05.471
Aagh!

01:24:05.847 --> 01:24:09.851
You bastard!

01:25:59.294 --> 01:26:03.339
You did the right thing.

01:26:03.381 --> 01:26:07.302
But I can't take you with me.

01:27:19.249 --> 01:27:21.584
Be OK, Mummy.

01:27:21.834 --> 01:27:25.546
